                   <li>Add buttons to toggle Focus Mode and Dark Mode on the statusbar.</li>
               </ul>
           </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.3.7" date="2017-10-09">
           <description>
               <p>Release: Small Fixes</p>
               <ul>
                   <li>Only small fixes in the app to have consistent design.</li>
               </ul>
           </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.3.6" date="2017-10-08">
           <description>
               <p>Release: When in Doubt, Hide your Status</p>
               <ul>
                   <li>Added a switch on the Preferences to show or hide the Statusbar in the current session</li>
               </ul>
           </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.3.5" date="2017-10-01">
